  "detailed_description": "<br><br>In the shadow of the bustling city there is a small, modest casino. Your gateway from rags to riches. Starting out as a miserable with nothing but greed, you're ready to turn this humble casino into a thriving casino empire. Every decision can lead to luck or madness and step into a world where your entrepreneurial spirit is the key to rising from zero to hero.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898270/extras/f1646373fa63d3af9d733f4080c9b580.webp?t=1758172877\" width=200 height=50 /></span><br><br>\"Increase Your Casino's Prestige\" is an engaging simulation game where you manage your own casino. Each item placed in the casino contributes to its prestige value, and customer reviews also affect this prestige. More customers and more money are the ultimate goals! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898270/extras/43591e61f8029fc747e95900864c8853.webp?t=1758172877\" width=200 height=50 /></span><br><br>\"Handling everything can be challenging, hire employees to ease your workload.\"<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898270/extras/e5699f22c6e8eb34282126cf7df2608d.poster.avif?t=1758172877\" width=570 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898270/extras/e5699f22c6e8eb34282126cf7df2608d.webm?t=1758172877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898270/extras/723ba1e688aca395b5e25db224761aa1.webp?t=1758172877\" width=200 height=50 /></span><br><br>\"A wide area is crucial for becoming wealthy. Expand your space 